an be used in areas where Bluetooth wireless use is prohibited or when battery power is low.</p>','sonicfuel-wireless-over-ear-headphones',NULL,NULL,NULL,'SonicFuel Wireless Over-Ear Headphones',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
